&quot;Amazons....&quot; she lifted her eyes to the proud warriors before her. &quot;We ride!&quot;   That was it....there was no time for any speaches.  Each amazon knew her calling and why she was here.  To each it would be a battle with her athelfi..and a battle within.   Hipp was wise enough to understand that.  <br>
Pulling her the reigns of her mare, she turned to ride towards the Northern Lands.  It would not be an fast journey...but they would race as quick as they could to their athelfi's sides. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazondelerium.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon DeLerium</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon</span><br>  Posts: 86<br> <font color=#993300>(8/20/01 8:50:30 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/deleriuml9/images/del2.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: We ride</span><hr size=1> ~ DeL placed he rmask over her face and nodded to Hippolyte. She let out a warcry then followed Hipp out of Themiscrya an on the road to the North. War is what DeL loved. However, she frowned under her mask though. Years ago there would of been more Themiscryians going with them. But times, she knew had changed.~ <p>~*Amazon DeLerium*~
